@startuml
title Composite

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Compose objects into tree structures for part-whole hierarchies. Treat both uniformly.

**Use when**: Tree-like structures (file systems, UI components).

**Key participants**: Component, Leaf, Composite.
endlegend

interface Component {
  +operation()
}

class Leaf
class Composite {
  +operation()
  +add(c: Component)
  +remove(c: Component)
  -children : List<Component>
}

Component <|.. Leaf
Component <|.. Composite
Composite *-- Component : children
@enduml